<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>639</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ yào zhī dào nǐ yào zhī dào, zhǔ de jīn tiān xīn.
 tā xǐ yuè wǒ men kuài kuài qǐ lái, kuài kuài qǐ lái jiù líng hún.
 yòng xīn líng jìng bài wàn yǒu de zhǔ zǎi.
 yòng chéng shí lái gē chàng, yǒng shì de dà jiù ēn.
 tā xǐ yuè wǒ men zuò hé píng de gē zi, fēi guò shān gāo shuǐ shēn.
 yì duān sì qǐ yáng wú mù rén, nǐ yào zhī dào zhǔ de jīn tiān xīn.</lyrics>
<title>nǐ yào zhī dào zhǔ de jīn tiān xīn 迦南639</title>
</song>